{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemelinkcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/AllLinkComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent04LinkB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDS\/documentation\/OUDS\/TokensProvider"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:colors:spaces:)"],"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider\/LinkComponentTokens-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of links","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"LinkComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"links","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Link"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B32ThemeLinkComponentTokensProviderC","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"title":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","symbolKind":"class","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for link component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the link component tokens you want.","","        override var linkSizeMinHeightMedium: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens.dimension600 }","","        override var linkColorArrowHover: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.colorRepositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var linkSpaceColumnGapIconSmall: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.spacePaddingInlineSpacious }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider: LinkComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"code":"CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}]},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(link: CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"or to an already existing theme for example:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(link: CustomLinkComponentTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}]},{"code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let linkComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, color and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let linkComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeLinkComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.9.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDS/documentation/OUDS/AllLinkComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Something which provides all component tokens of link"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllLinkComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"TokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4OUDS14TokensProviderP"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"LinkComponentTokens","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:19OUD